'''安哥洛卡象龜'''（[[學名|學名]]：{{lang|la|''Astrochelys yniphora''}}）又名'''馬達加斯加陸龜'''，'''安哥洛卡陸龜'''，俗名'''犁頭龜'''，是[[馬達加斯加|馬達加斯加]]西北部[[特有種|特有]]的一種[[龜|龜]]<ref name="Juvik">{{cite web | last1 = Juvik | first1 = J.O. | last2 = Meier | first2 = D.E. | last3 = McKeown | first3 = S. | title = Captive Husbandry and Conservation of the Madagascar Ploughshare Tortoise, Geochelone yniphora | url = http://www.tortoise.org/archives/yniphora.html | publisher = Proceedings of the First International Symposium on Turtles & Tortoises: Conservation and Captive Husbandry | year = 1991 | accessdate = 29 December 2010 | archive-date = 2011-01-09 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20110109031901/http://tortoise.org/archives/yniphora.html | dead-url = yes }}</ref>，屬於陸龜科的一員<ref name = "Fritz">{{Cite journal
